{"tid":1426293,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［合法］良心抗稅運動","createTime":"2019-08-07T01:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T02:27:03.000Z","uid":63178,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8aa81f5b0297ca174ce8e1ffb897f2863a2a7d10","tid":1426293,"uid":63178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KdAsAHF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKdAsAHF.png&h=df2e0994&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果咁多位同路人一蚊一蚊咁用信用卡交稅，扣埋card centre既手續費，理論上政府係一蚊都收唔到<br />\n其實呢招雨傘後都用過，只係唔夠人咁做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nReference: <br />\n<a href=\"http://taxresistancehk.blogpost.com/2014/12/blog-post_95.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftaxresistancehk.blogpost.com%2F2014%2F12%2Fblog-post_95.html&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apKnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=8052c28d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">taxresistancehk.blogpost.com/2014/12/blog-post_95.html</a>"},{"pid":"617211325350b59eaac3e69c70dc40ee9e82f45f","tid":1426293,"uid":226421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237150fc1bcf72200e2182020763b71d4dcb5a87","tid":1426293,"uid":93940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:48:23.000Z","msg":"記得逐蚊數清楚呀。<br />\n交多咗，稅局係咪要開支票退返嘅呢？"},{"pid":"d553bb2e43393dd7f1b20febdf33a6880828bdfe","tid":1426293,"uid":63178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"237150fc1bcf72200e2182020763b71d4dcb5a87","tid":1426293,"uid":93940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:48:23.000Z","msg":"記得逐蚊數清楚呀。<br />\n交多咗，稅局係咪要開支票退返嘅呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:17:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59db5c0a8945c1f60f1738b82f2f9b7456018b39","tid":1426293,"uid":276954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:27:03.000Z","msg":"我唔交稅住...<br />\n<br />\n唔交稅點可能?遲交都要加多5%。<br />\n<br />\n但你嘅評稅1日未完成,政府都唔可以開張稅單嚟收稅。<br />\n<br />\n打電話通知收唔到報稅單。拖一拖。<br />\n<br />\n張報稅表未簽名佢都唔可以開始。<br />\n<br />\n一於拖得就拖。吹呀!"}]}